Witness the Legend				KEY:Domain Power ~ Witness the Legend				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.DomainPower							SOURCEPAGE:p.24	DESC:As a move action, you can extol the virtues of yourself or an ally within 60 feet that you can see. This causes the target to shed light like a torch for 1 minute, and while the effect lasts, you can expend a daily use of your touch of glory domain ability as an immediate action to add 1d6 to an attack, saving throw, skill check, or ability check attempted by the target; for a roll to confirm a critical hit or save against a fear effect, you instead add 1d12. You can use this ability %1 times day|(DomainGloryLVL-4)/4
